					<div class="post-info">
						<p>
							<span class="time">April 17, 2013</span>
															<span class="author">by <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/author/mktgeistmike/" title="Posts by mktgeistmike" rel="author">mktgeistmike</a></span>
																						<span class="post-comments"><a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/2013/04/17/silver-update-41613-force-majeure/#respond" title="Comment on Silver Update 4/16/13 Force&nbsp;Majeure">Leave a comment</a></span>
